BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:We will be hiking our newly built Echo Canyon Trail to learn ab
 out the geological process that created McCormick's Creek Including limesto
 ne formations and glacier activity. This trail is less tha.5 \,ile with ove
 rlooks of the waterfall and Echo Canyon. We will begin our hik from the Nat
 ure Center.
