END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:We will be hiking our newly built\, accessible Echo Canyon Trai
 l to learn about the geological process that created McCormick's Creek incl
 uding limestone formations and glacier activity. This trail is less than .5
  mile with overlooks of the waterfall and Echo Canyon. We will begin our hi
 ke from the Nature Center.
