BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:March is baby season for our local foxes in Indiana. A mama fox
  can have up to 5 pups. These fast quick animals are hard to find but beaut
 iful to see. Join our fox mug craft and learn more about foxes at the Natur
 e Center. This craft is best for ages 8 and up.
DTEND:20260307T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260317T230318Z
DTSTART:20260307T150000Z
