BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:A 1.5-mile moderate hike. Gate fees will apply to attend progra
 ms. Join David Mow\, invasive specialist and master gardener instructor\, f
 or a hike at Owen County’s largest waterfall and observe the different habi
 tats along the creek as staff help identify flowers along the way. Meet: 26
 05 N. Cataract Road\, Spencer\, Cataract Falls State Recreation Area
