BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:Register online at: https://runsignup.com/.../Spencer/FriendsMc
 CormicksCreek5k\n\nThis is a Mag 7 Series Race.\n\nThose registered and pai
 d by March 15th(by mail) or April 3rd(online) will receive a race shirt. Sh
 irts available after that while supplies last.\n\nPacket Pick Up: 7:00-8:15
 am at the Nature Center\n\nRace starts promptly at 8:30am\n\nAwards followi
 ng the race. Prizes to top male and female 5K overall runners and walkers. 
 Awards granted to top 2 age group winners in 5K run and first age group win
 ners in 5K walk.\n\n***NEW THIS YEAR: Post-race Pancakes and Sausage Breakf
 ast available for $5. Please purchase by 4/15/2026 so we know how much to b
 uy.\n\nAll proceeds from the race and the breakfast will be used to develop
  and support projects and events that help preserve\, restore\, manage\, an
 d interpret the natural and cultural heritage and recreational opportunitie
 s of McCormick’s Creek State Park
DTEND:20260418T133000Z
DTSTAMP:20260317T230318Z
DTSTART:20260418T123000Z
GEO:39.286051;-86.726529
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park
SEQUENCE:0
