CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:Come join Brown County Bluebird Club to build a bluebird box to
  help support native birds. This workshop cost $10 a box. Please bring cash
  to pay for your birdhouse. You can build your box at Pine Bluff Shelter. T
 his workshop requires pre-registration. Please register at b4bluebirds@gmai
 l.com. Come build your bluebird box at the Nature Center.
