BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Arts\, Blues\, and BBQ at McCormick’s Creek State P
 ark. All events will be held at the Nature Center parking lot. Shop at our 
 local art vendor booths. Bring a lawn chair to enjoy live blues music from 
 our band line up listed below. Smokin’ Jacks food truck will be onsite offe
 ring BBQ to purchase. Sweet Valley Ice Cream will be offering hand scooped 
 ice-cream treats. The Canyon Inn will offer walking tacos\, hot dogs\, beer
 \, and wine for purchase.
DTEND:20260912T220000Z
