BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:(Event) Join the White River Valley Archaeological Association 
 for a family fun day of Native American Culture. Learn how to flint knap or
  throw spears used by various tribes for hunting. Visit Exhibits to learn a
 rcheological facts. All programs are happening at the Nature Center.
