DESCRIPTION:Hop and slither to the Nature Center to see our resident reptil
 es chow down on bugs and mice. Learn cool facts about Indiana's native amph
 ibians and reptiles.   \n\nNature Center is open every day from 10 am-5 pm 
 EDT May-October.\n\nClosed on Tuesdays & Wednesdays November-April\n\nUpcom
 ing programs can be seen by visiting on.in.gov/mccormickscreek\n\nOur inter
 pretive programs are designed to entertain and enrich folks of all ages. Ch
 ildren under 12 must have an adult with them at the programs.\n\nRegistrati
 on is not required for programs (unless stated). All our programs are free 
 (unless otherwise noted). They are open to the public after paying the park
  entrance fee.\n\nAll our Interpretive programs are listed in Eastern Dayli
 ght Savings Time.\n\n*Note that during peak visitation times\, entry into o
 ur park might be delayed. The drive to the Nature Center can take 8 minutes
 . Please plan accordingly.\n\nIf you need more information\, call 812-829-2
 235 ext. 2
DTEND:20261115T193000Z
DTSTAMP:20260317T230319Z
DTSTART:20261115T190000Z
GEO:39.286051;-86.726529
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, Nature Center
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Cold Blooded Buffet\, McCormick's Creek State Park
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51499322043912
URL:https://events.in.gov/event/cold-blooded-buffet-mccormicks-creek-state-
 park
END:VEVENT
