BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Events
DESCRIPTION:Come to the Canyon Inn vote for your favorite Christmas quilts 
 made by your local artist. Bid on your favorite themed basket in our silent
  auction. Paintings of your favorite park features will be available to pur
 chase. All donations and proceeds go to the Friends of McCormick's Creek.
DTEND:20261212T233000Z
DTSTAMP:20260317T230319Z
